@startuml rankDescVec-读取路径-6层调用链路
' ============================================================
' rankDescVec_ 读取路径 — 6层调用链路时序图
'
' 覆盖:
'   - V2 正常路径
'   - V1 fallback
'   - 初始化路径: CollComm 构造 + BuildRankDescVec 数据灌入
'
' 语法注意事项:
'   - == 分隔线内不能用 ()
'   - group/loop 块内不能放 note
'   - 避免 Unicode 特殊符号
' ============================================================

skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ParticipantPadding 40
skinparam SequenceBoxBorderColor #555555

title rankDescVec_ 读取路径 — HcclGetRankDescList 6层调用链路

actor "C 调用者\n应用层" as User

box "C API 层" #E8F5E9
    participant "HcclGetRankDescList\nhccl_independent_rank_graph.cc:378" as Api
end box

box "V2/V1 分发" #FFF3E0
    participant "HCCLV2_FUNC_RUN\nparam_check_basic_v2.h:18" as Macro
end box

box "hccl 命名空间 / V2 框架层" #E3F2FD
    participant "hccl::hcclComm\nhccl_comm_pub.h" as Comm
    participant "hccl::CollComm\ncoll_comm.h:33" as CollComm
    participant "hccl::RankGraph\n虚基类 / rank_graph_base.h:23" as Base
    participant "hccl::RankGraphV2\nrank_graph_v2.h:16" as V2
end box

box "Hccl 命名空间 / Legacy 实现层" #F3E5F5
    participant "Hccl::IRankGraph\nrank_graph_interface.h:20" as IFace
    participant "Hccl::RankGraph\n数据源 / rank_gph.h:33" as DataSrc
    database "rankDescVec_\nvector<RankDesc>" as Vec
end box

== V2 正常路径 : isSupportV2 == true ==

User -> Api: HcclGetRankDescList\n  comm, &descList, &descNum

group 参数校验
    Api -> Api: CHK_PTR_NULL comm\nCHK_PTR_NULL descList\nCHK_PTR_NULL descNum
end

Api -> Macro: HCCLV2_FUNC_RUN lambda

group 宏展开 : V2 运行时判断
    Macro -> Macro: hrtGetHcclV2Support\n-> isSupportV2 == true
end

note over Api, Macro: isSupportV2 == true\n执行 lambda 并直接 return

Api -> Comm: static_cast<hccl::hcclComm*>(comm)
activate Comm

Api -> Comm: GetCollComm()
Comm --> Api: CollComm*
deactivate Comm

Api -> CollComm: GetRankGraph()
activate CollComm
CollComm -> CollComm: rankgraph_.get()
note right of CollComm
  rankgraph_ =
  unique_ptr<hccl::RankGraph>
  实际对象 = RankGraphV2
end note
CollComm --> Api: hccl::RankGraph*
deactivate CollComm

Api -> Base: rankGraph->GetRankDescList\n  descList, descNum
note over Base: 虚函数调用

group 虚函数派发
    Base -[#0000FF]> V2: 虚表派发 -> RankGraphV2
    activate V2

    V2 -> IFace: pImpl->GetRankDescList\n  descList, descNum / 参数透传
    activate IFace

    group IRankGraph : void* 还原 + const_cast 桥接
        IFace -> IFace: CHK_PTR_NULL descList\nCHK_PTR_NULL descNum\nCHK_PTR_NULL rankGraphPtr_

        IFace -> IFace: static_cast<RankGraph*>\n  rankGraphPtr_\n  void* -> Hccl::RankGraph*

        IFace -> DataSrc: GetRankDescVec()
        activate DataSrc
        DataSrc -> Vec: return rankDescVec_
        DataSrc --> IFace: const vector<RankDesc>&
        deactivate DataSrc

        IFace -> Vec: vec.data()
        Vec --> IFace: const RankDesc*

        IFace -> IFace: *descList =\n  const_cast<RankDesc*>\n    vec.data()
    end

    note right of IFace
      const_cast 去掉 const
      暴露内部裸指针
      零拷贝, 调用者禁止释放
    end note

    IFace -> Vec: vec.size()
    Vec --> IFace: size_t
    IFace -> IFace: *descNum =\n  static_cast<uint32_t>\n    vec.size()

    IFace --> V2: HCCL_SUCCESS
    deactivate IFace

    V2 --> Base: HCCL_SUCCESS
    deactivate V2
end

Base --> Api: HCCL_SUCCESS
Api --> User: HCCL_SUCCESS\n*descList -> rankDescVec_.data()\n*descNum  = vec.size()

== V1 fallback 路径 : isSupportV2 == false ==

User -> Api: HcclGetRankDescList ...

Api -> Macro: HCCLV2_FUNC_RUN lambda
Macro -> Macro: hrtGetHcclV2Support\n-> isSupportV2 == false
note over Macro: lambda 不执行\ndo-while 结束\n控制流继续到 V1 代码

Api -> Api: HCCL_ERROR\n"V1 path not supported"
Api --> User: HCCL_E_NOT_SUPPORT
note over User, Api: V1 通信域不支持\nRankGraphV1 未重写\nGetRankDescList 虚函数

== 初始化路径 : 通信域创建时 / 独立于查询 ==

note over Comm, IFace: 此段与查询路径独立\n在通信域初始化时执行

Comm -> CollComm: collComm_->Init\n  void* rankGraph,\n  binHandle, cclBuffer, config
activate CollComm

CollComm -> V2: rankgraph_ =\n  make_unique<RankGraphV2>\n    rankGraph
activate V2

V2 -> IFace: pImpl =\n  make_unique<IRankGraph>\n    rankGraphPtr
activate IFace

IFace -> IFace: rankGraphPtr_ = rankGraphPtr
note right of IFace: void* 存储\n后续 static_cast 还原

deactivate IFace
deactivate V2
deactivate CollComm

== BuildRankDescVec Data Fill ==

DataSrc -> DataSrc: BuildRankDescVec rankTable

group BuildRankDescVec detail
    DataSrc -> Vec: assign count RankDesc{}
    DataSrc -> DataSrc: populate all 8 fields from rankTable + peers_
    DataSrc -> DataSrc: ReparseGroupedPlaneForOcsMesh ocsPlaneId/Num
end

@enduml
